snippet.title: Foo Fighters - Times Like These | Soul AI Cover
snippet.description:
Times Like These by Foo Fighters twisted into Soul music!

Like what you hear? Help keep the party going!
https://tiptopjar.com/TwistedMusicStudio

Lyrics:

I, I'm a one way motorway
I'm the one that drives away, follows you back home
I, I'm a street light shining
I'm a white light blinding bright, burning off and on
Uh-huh

It's times like these you learn to live again
It's times like these you give and give again
It's times like these you learn to love again
It's times like these time and time again

I, I'm a new day rising
I'm a brand new sky to hang the stars upon tonight
But I, I'm a little divided
Do I stay or run away and leave it all behind?
Uh-huh

It's times like these you learn to love again
